casebody.data:
Eisler, Respondent, v. Union Transfer & Storage Co. et al.. Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November, 1889.) Appeal from seventh district court.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Van Hoesen, J.

H. C. Andrews, for appellants. J. Martin, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment reversed, new trial ordered, costs to abide the event.
